Package: fhc
Title: Fit Flexible-Hazards Cure Models
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Can", "Xie", , "can.xie@uth.tmc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4170-1247")),
    person("Xuelin", "Huang", email = "xlhuang@mdanderson.org", role = "aut"),
    person("Ruosha", "Li", email = "ruosha.li@uth.tmc.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: A flexible-hazards cure model (non-mixture cure model) with the property of handling non-proportional hazards structure of one or more variables 
    in a survival-cure data set can be esaily estimated by applying the function. Cure rates and estimated survival curves can be obtained as well.
